      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys Mechanical) operates under a documented QMS with version control, regression testing, and audit trails consistent with FDA 21 CFR Part 820 requirements.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 was used under a validated installation with documented QMS procedures. Regression test suite executed prior to analysis; no anomalies detected. Version-controlled input decks archived in the sponsor's PLM system."
